{"tid":2399331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國前國務卿舒爾茨逝世　享年100歲","createTime":"2021-02-08T04:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T09:54:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acdc4011dc4df63e6cffcb7eb4b3c37f219ecdf6","tid":2399331,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"美國前國務卿舒爾茨去世，享年100歲。他効力過三位共和黨籍總統，在列根時代擔任國務卿期間，對美國政府冷戰末期的外交政策發揮重要影響力。<br />\n<br />\n1920年生於紐約的舒爾茨是經濟學者出身，上世紀五十年代加入艾森豪威爾政府擔任經濟顧問。<br />\n<br />\n到尼克遜出任總統時，舒爾茨先後出掌勞工部及財政部，他在1982年重返政府，擔任列根政府的國務卿，當時美國與蘇聯關係跌至谷底。<br />\n<br />\n在舒爾茨的努力下，美蘇高層恢復接觸，促成兩國在1987年簽署中程導彈條約，雙方銷毀近2700支導彈，被視為冷戰其中一個重要轉捩點，舒爾茨在回憶錄甚至指冷戰是在列根年代終結。<br />\n<br />\n舒爾茨在任國務卿時，亦提出對恐怖分子先發制人的策略，這個政策雖然當時未獲注意，但到喬治布殊執政時成為反恐戰主軸之一，在2003年美國出兵伊拉克前，舒爾茨曾表明支持出兵。<br />\n<br />\n美國胡佛研究所周日宣布舒爾茨在加州史丹福大學的寓所逝世，享年100歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=423368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423368&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUimsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=ebf96cd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423368&h=28ab424d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=423368</a>"},{"pid":"53cff921515ceb825ba9614e14e74eeaf30ec1f9","tid":2399331,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip"},{"pid":"7b90385ea1a189f8a28d7254fbe0ef8c306dde85","tid":2399331,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"ceab4bbba8bd11de7301b991d280f30e595ae720","tid":2399331,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"希望ccp 都可以died at 100"},{"pid":"5fd6bdc66a20734ab1896324671435f85bebe7d8","tid":2399331,"uid":85461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"strong men create good times"},{"pid":"0da09d293c4ef49aa4d73f42b96e938206d59f2e","tid":2399331,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008650024152e015448651310aea5f37f1996546","tid":2399331,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}